<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="35" type="ecology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="35">Ecology and distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="35">
Epilithic in a mountain river with oligotrophic waters. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bing Liu &amp; D. M. Williams" authorityYear="2022" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Surirellaceae" genus="Surirella" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Surirella suiningensis" order="Surirellales" pageId="0" pageNumber="35" phylum="Bacillariophyta" rank="species" species="suiningensis">
